# Mini spec — ZSAH1_WORKDAYS (live-spike review target)

ZSAH1_WORKDAYS is a workday calculation utility report. lcl_workdays=>calc(
iv_from, iv_to, it_holidays optional ) must return the count of Monday-Friday
days in [iv_from, iv_to] excluding the given holidays; an inverted range
(iv_from > iv_to) returns 0. The public signature must stay unchanged.
A local FOR TESTING class must cover the weekday/weekend/holiday/same-day/
inverted-range cases. Scope of this review: logic and style sanity only.
